---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="SiteIntelica Privacy Policy">
  <div class="container prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}</p>
    
    <p>
      At SiteIntelica, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines what information we collect, how it is used, and how we protect your data when you use our website.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect minimal personal data. When you use the SiteIntelica "Spy" tool:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Public URLs:</strong> We process the fully public URLs you submit for analysis. This data is processed temporarily to fetch the technology stack but is not associated with your personal identity.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> We may use privacy-respecting analytics tools to understand how our site is used (e.g., page views, general geographic region) to improve the service.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use the Information</h2>
    <p>
      The data collected is used solely for the following purposes:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide the technology analysis service you requested.</li>
      <li>To identify usage trends and improve the UI/UX of our tool.</li>
      <li>To monitor and prevent abuse of our API endpoints.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal identification information to others. The URL analysis happens server-side, and results are returned directly to your browser session.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Our analysis engine (Wappalyzer Core) visits external websites to gather technology profiles. However, we do not share the fact that <em>you</em> specifically initiated the search with those external websites. We act merely as an intermediary scraper.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      SiteIntelica has the discretion to update this privacy policy at any time. When we do, we will revise the updated date at the top of this page. We encourage Users to frequently check this page for any changes.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/about">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
